snippet.title: Gameplay: Killer Instinct for the Arcade (1994)
snippet.description:
Another trip down nostalgia lane...this time I'm bringing you a gameplay video of the 1994 arcade smash hit Killer Instinct. I decided to show footage of the arcade version since most of us are already familiar with the SNES version of the game.

This is definitely one of my all time favorite fighting games so I hope you enjoy the video. Please note that I'm very rusty in the game so don't expect any expert type gameplay...we're not in 1995 anymore ;-)
